      "body" : "Hey, I am trying to do a task only if the background image of an image button is a certain drawable resource. How can I compare... I&#39;ve tried <code>if(buttonBackground.equals(R.drawable.myDrawable))</code> where <code>Drawable buttonBackground = myButton.getBackground();</code>I get this error:  <a href=\"http://snag.gy/weYgA.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">snag.gy/weYgA.jpg</a>"
