    "body" : "<pre><code>RelativeLayout relativeLayout;  //declare this globally\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>now, inside any function like onCreate, onResume</p>\n\n<pre><code>relativeLayout = new RelativeLayout(this);  \nrelativeLayout.setBackgroundResource(R.drawable.view); //or whatever your image is\nsetContentView(relativeLayout); //you might be forgetting this\n</code></pre>\n"
